===Additional specifications=== * Per ''ASUS'''s product page: :indicates the device has two processors: :one for WiFi and the other for ADSL. :The device has RP-SMA connectors. * ''Antenna'': 3x detachable antenna (2dBi) * ''Ports'': xDSL: 1x ADSL2+ (RJ11) :WAN: 1x GbE (RJ45) 10/100/1000 BaseT :LAN: 4x GbE (RJ45) 10/100/1000 BaseT :USB: 2x USB 2.0 * ''Power Adapter'': :AC Input : 100~240V (50~60HZ) :DC Output : 12V/2A *''Dimensions (W x H x D)'': 207 mm x 35.5 mm x 148.8 mm *''Weight'': 500 g
==See also== *[[ASUS DSL-AC52U]] - AC750 (VDSL2/ADSL2/2+, GbE LAN, USB 2.0) *[[ASUS DSL-AC68U]] - AC1900 (VDSL2/ADSL2/2+, GbE LAN, USB 3.0)
